{
  "stem": "7177.3",
  "chunk_idx": 2,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 6.8,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "He came from the background, let's say, and he came close to me, and he said, you're almost there, Betty.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "And we hadn't said a word all these hours.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "Nobody had spoken to each other, because they think of being-- you know, if anything would have happened, they would have gone, and we would have been picked up.",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "I didn't want anything to-- nobody wanted anything to happen to them.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "They had risked their lives already enough.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "So he came finally to me, and he said, Betty you're almost there.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "And I said, well, if I have to get off this bike, I'm going to fall, I can tell you that already.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "He said, you're not going to fall.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "Just wait a second.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "And he traveled-- he rode his bike for maybe 10, 15, 20 feet, 20 yards ahead of me, and threw his bike on the ground and waited for me and caught me in his arms.",
      "word_count": 35
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 27,
      "text": "And I did not fall.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 28,
      "text": "He caught-- caught the bicycle, my tandem bike.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 29,
      "text": "And that was very close to the house where we spent our second year in hiding.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 30,
      "text": "The people-- this was a-- a-- what should I say-- a farmhouse.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 31,
      "text": "An elderly couple in their '80s.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 32,
      "text": "And the first one we saw was my brother, Harry.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 33,
      "text": "He had been there already maybe a month in that same house.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 34,
      "text": "The people, I would like to describe them to you.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 35,
      "text": "In their '80s.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I do not remember their-- we-- we called them Opa-- Opa means grandpa-- Garben was their last name.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Garben.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Garben.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "G-A-R-B-E-N.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And the lady was at least in the 80s.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And she didn't really know what was going on, but she didn't have to know, because everybody else took care of us.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "We came into the house.",
      "word_count": 5
    }
  ],
